name: language_sql_data_trailing_non_breaking_space
description: |
  The value ends with U+00A0 NO-BREAK SPACE rather than ASCII space. Form
  trimming, SQL collations, fixed-width columns, and application comparisons may
  disagree about whether it is significant.
format: hex
decode-as: utf8
unicode-meta:
  code-units: 7
  code-points: 6
  scalar-values: 6
  legacy-grapheme-clusters: 6
  extended-grapheme-clusters: 6
tags:
  - "language"
  - "sql"
  - "sql-data"
  - "utf8"
  - "non-breaking-space"
  - "trailing-whitespace"
  - "normalization"
  - "collation"
---
"admin" c2 a0
